      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years, so it's ready to hit the road with you today! It drives super smoothly and is just waiting for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and won't break the bank, this is the one. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
